name: High Valley Cyberpunktacos
description:
High Valley Cyberpunktacos

INTERACTIVE AUDIO JACKATHON ENTRY

Controls:

W: up

S: Down

A: Left

D: Rigth

Q: Forward

E: Backward

Hold Mouse Rigth click and pan to look around

Grab grey circles to earn points and time, red dots lower your time, if you run out of time gameover. Make some big score to brag about!
